Package gameObjects

Class GameObject

java.lang.Object
gameObjects.GameObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
GameLogic
Direct Known Subclasses:
Block, Camera, Entity, Event, InvisibleObject, Shape
public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements GameLogic
The Class GameObject. GameObjects are all objects that are used in the game (characters, blocks, etc)
